verse.lines:
{lang-eng}Entho goppa nityamaina poorna rakshana ide
Nirlakshinchina thappinchukonavu
Pondu prabhu rakshana{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Mana prabhuve rakshana shrungamaaye
Shatruvu nodincha shakthi mantudu
Manaku jayamu nichchunu{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Prabhuve mana rakshana shailamaaye
Dhrudaparache naayane manala
Paadamula stiraparachenu{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Prabhuve mana rakshana durghamaaye
Thanayande manaku poorna bhadratha
Priyamaara dayacheyunu{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Prabhuve mana rakshana kedemaaye
Dustuni baarinundi thaappinchi
Padilamugaa rakshinchunu{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Prabhuve mana rakshana shirastraanamu
Jeevamu dwaaraa rakshana kanuparacha
Aashathoda nundumu{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Rakshana paathra pongi porluchunnadi
Rakshana ootache santhrupthi kaligi
Paripoornatha neevegaa{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Rakshana vastramu dharimpa jesenuga
Neethi vastramunu dharimpajesi
Anandimpa jesenu{/lang-eng}
